record_data.record_plain_text:
Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service
Susquehanna Nuclear, LLC ("Susquehanna") provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ("Reactive Supply Service") from various generating units in the PPL Zone to the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ("PJM"). This Rate Schedule consists of four separate tariff rate sections, one for each generating unit, and sets forth Susquehanna's revenue requirements for the provision of Reactive Supply Service to PJM within the PPL Zone consistent with Schedule 2 of the PJM Open Access Transmission Tariff. This Rate Schedule shall be effective on December 1, 2016.
Susquehanna Unit 1
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $2,916,083.34.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $2,916,083.34 / 12 = $243,006.94.
Susquehanna Unit 2
1. TOTAL REVENUE REQUIREMENT
Total Annual Revenue Requirement is $2,874,834.43.
Total Monthly Revenue Requirement is $2,874,834.43 / 12 = $239,569.54.
